data.description: SALTWATER POOL and so much more. Come see this 4/2 home in desirable Lofton Pointe. Large ticket items replaced: New Roof 2023, newer HVAC (3 years old approx) and Water Heater (1 year approx). Home offers formal living, dining and flex space or office (currently used as dining). Master suite offers laminate floors, plantation shutters, his and her closets, dual vanities, walk in shower, garden tub, linen closet and extra storage. Laminate floors throughout except secondary bedrooms and tile in kitchen and baths. Enjoy the outdoors and private setting in your backyard and take a dip on those warm summer days. Citrus plants and fully fenced yard for your little ones and/or pets. Close to shopping, dining, movie theater and just a short drive to the beautiful beaches of Amelia Island, Historic downtown with a variety of shops, restaurants, and entertainment. Approx.25 minutes to Jax International Airport. Vsit this home today and envision poolside entertainment with family and friends.
